subject: Updates to Discord's Policies
body: Transparency is important to us, and we want to let you know what's changing ahead of time so you can learn about what's new. These changes will take effect on March 27, 2023.

subject: Confirm Your Font Awesome Account Email Address
body: You're so close to using your first Font Awesome Kit and there's a Font Awesome account waiting just for you. We just need you to confirm your email address to finish setting you up! We promise, it'll just take a sec.

subject: Your GitLens Pro Trial is ending!
body: Hey there,Today is the last day of your GitLens Pro trial. To continue using the powerful GitLens+ features like the Commit Graph, richer integration with GitLab Self-Managed, Worktrees and Visual File History with your private repos, upgrade to a paid GitLens plan. If you don't need access to GitLens+ features with private repos, no action is needed! You can continue to use these features for free with public repos forever.
